-- The `Structural` predicate: "no `Agen` subterm anywhere".

data Structural : вҲҖ {A B} вҶ’ HomTerm A B вҶ’ Set where
  structural-id : вҲҖ {A} вҶ’ Structural (id {A})
  structural-О»вҮ’ : вҲҖ {A} вҶ’ Structural (О»вҮ’ {A})
  structural-О»вҮҗ : вҲҖ {A} вҶ’ Structural (О»вҮҗ {A})
  structural-ПҒвҮ’ : вҲҖ {A} вҶ’ Structural (ПҒвҮ’ {A})
  structural-ПҒвҮҗ : вҲҖ {A} вҶ’ Structural (ПҒвҮҗ {A})
  structural-ОұвҮ’ : вҲҖ {A B C} вҶ’ Structural (ОұвҮ’ {A} {B} {C})
  structural-ОұвҮҗ : вҲҖ {A B C} вҶ’ Structural (ОұвҮҗ {A} {B} {C})
  structural-Пғ  : вҲҖ {A B} вҰғ s : Symm вүӨ Symm вҰ„
                вҶ’ Structural (Пғ {A = A} {B = B} вҰғ s вҰ„)
  structural-вҲҳ  : вҲҖ {A B C} {h : HomTerm B C} {k : HomTerm A B}
                вҶ’ Structural h вҶ’ Structural k
                вҶ’ Structural (h вҲҳ k)
  structural-вҠ—  : вҲҖ {A B C D} {h : HomTerm A B} {k : HomTerm C D}
                вҶ’ Structural h вҶ’ Structural k
                вҶ’ Structural (h вҠ—вӮҒ k)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- `NoSigma`: predicate "no `Пғ` subterm anywhere".  Strictly stronger
-- than `Structural` (which allows Пғ); morphisms satisfying `NoSigma`
-- live in the Mac Lane fragment, where coherence is fully constructive
-- via `Categories.MonoidalCoherence.Solver.solveM`.

data NoSigma : вҲҖ {A B} вҶ’ HomTerm A B вҶ’ Set where
  nosigma-id : вҲҖ {A} вҶ’ NoSigma (id {A})
  nosigma-О»вҮ’ : вҲҖ {A} вҶ’ NoSigma (О»вҮ’ {A})
  nosigma-О»вҮҗ : вҲҖ {A} вҶ’ NoSigma (О»вҮҗ {A})
  nosigma-ПҒвҮ’ : вҲҖ {A} вҶ’ NoSigma (ПҒвҮ’ {A})
  nosigma-ПҒвҮҗ : вҲҖ {A} вҶ’ NoSigma (ПҒвҮҗ {A})
  nosigma-ОұвҮ’ : вҲҖ {A B C} вҶ’ NoSigma (ОұвҮ’ {A} {B} {C})
  nosigma-ОұвҮҗ : вҲҖ {A B C} вҶ’ NoSigma (ОұвҮҗ {A} {B} {C})
  nosigma-вҲҳ  : вҲҖ {A B C} {h : HomTerm B C} {k : HomTerm A B}
             вҶ’ NoSigma h вҶ’ NoSigma k
             вҶ’ NoSigma (h вҲҳ k)
  nosigma-вҠ—  : вҲҖ {A B C D} {h : HomTerm A B} {k : HomTerm C D}
             вҶ’ NoSigma h вҶ’ NoSigma k
             вҶ’ NoSigma (h вҠ—вӮҒ k)

NoSigmaвҶ’Structural : вҲҖ {A B} {f : HomTerm A B} вҶ’ NoSigma f вҶ’ Structural f
NoSigmaвҶ’Structural nosigma-id      = structural-id
NoSigmaвҶ’Structural nosigma-О»вҮ’      = structural-О»вҮ’
NoSigmaвҶ’Structural nosigma-О»вҮҗ      = structural-О»вҮҗ
NoSigmaвҶ’Structural nosigma-ПҒвҮ’      = structural-ПҒвҮ’
NoSigmaвҶ’Structural nosigma-ПҒвҮҗ      = structural-ПҒвҮҗ
NoSigmaвҶ’Structural nosigma-ОұвҮ’      = structural-ОұвҮ’
NoSigmaвҶ’Structural nosigma-ОұвҮҗ      = structural-ОұвҮҗ
NoSigmaвҶ’Structural (nosigma-вҲҳ h k) = structural-вҲҳ (NoSigmaвҶ’Structural h)
                                                   (NoSigmaвҶ’Structural k)
NoSigmaвҶ’Structural (nosigma-вҠ— h k) = structural-вҠ— (NoSigmaвҶ’Structural h)
                                                   (NoSigmaвҶ’Structural k)

-- Decide whether a structural term contains at least one `Пғ`.
HasSigma? : вҲҖ {A B} {f : HomTerm A B} вҶ’ Structural f вҶ’ NoSigma f вҠҺ вҠӨ
HasSigma? structural-id        = injвӮҒ nosigma-id
HasSigma? structural-О»вҮ’        = injвӮҒ nosigma-О»вҮ’
HasSigma? structural-О»вҮҗ        = injвӮҒ nosigma-О»вҮҗ
HasSigma? structural-ПҒвҮ’        = injвӮҒ nosigma-ПҒвҮ’
HasSigma? structural-ПҒвҮҗ        = injвӮҒ nosigma-ПҒвҮҗ
HasSigma? structural-ОұвҮ’        = injвӮҒ nosigma-ОұвҮ’
HasSigma? structural-ОұвҮҗ        = injвӮҒ nosigma-ОұвҮҗ
HasSigma? structural-Пғ         = injвӮӮ tt
HasSigma? (structural-вҲҳ sh sk) with HasSigma? sh | HasSigma? sk
... | injвӮҒ nh | injвӮҒ nk = injвӮҒ (nosigma-вҲҳ nh nk)
... | _       | _       = injвӮӮ tt
HasSigma? (structural-вҠ— sh sk) with HasSigma? sh | HasSigma? sk
... | injвӮҒ nh | injвӮҒ nk = injвӮҒ (nosigma-вҠ— nh nk)
... | _       | _       = injвӮӮ tt

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Atomic structural constructors are structural.  (The `Agen` atomic
-- constructor is excluded вҖ” it has `nE вүЎ 1` and is handled separately.)

Atomic-non-AgenвҶ’Structural
  : вҲҖ {A B} {f : HomTerm A B}
  вҶ’ Atomic f вҶ’ nE вҹӘ f вҹ« вүЎ 0 вҶ’ Structural f
Atomic-non-AgenвҶ’Structural (atomic-Agen _)   ()
Atomic-non-AgenвҶ’Structural atomic-id         _ = structural-id
Atomic-non-AgenвҶ’Structural atomic-О»вҮ’         _ = structural-О»вҮ’
Atomic-non-AgenвҶ’Structural atomic-О»вҮҗ         _ = structural-О»вҮҗ
Atomic-non-AgenвҶ’Structural atomic-ПҒвҮ’         _ = structural-ПҒвҮ’
Atomic-non-AgenвҶ’Structural atomic-ПҒвҮҗ         _ = structural-ПҒвҮҗ
Atomic-non-AgenвҶ’Structural atomic-ОұвҮ’         _ = structural-ОұвҮ’
Atomic-non-AgenвҶ’Structural atomic-ОұвҮҗ         _ = structural-ОұвҮҗ
Atomic-non-AgenвҶ’Structural (atomic-Пғ вҰғ s вҰ„)  _ = structural-Пғ вҰғ s вҰ„

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Main syntactic lemma: a 0-edge HomTerm is structural.
--
-- Proceeds by induction on `g`.  For atomic constructors, route via
-- `Atomic-non-AgenвҶ’Structural` (and explicitly rule out `Agen`).  For
-- compound constructors, split the additive 0 into both summands.

nE-0вҶ’Structural
  : вҲҖ {A B} (g : HomTerm A B) вҶ’ nE вҹӘ g вҹ« вүЎ 0 вҶ’ Structural g
nE-0вҶ’Structural (Agen _)              ()
nE-0вҶ’Structural id                    _ = structural-id
nE-0вҶ’Structural О»вҮ’                    _ = structural-О»вҮ’
nE-0вҶ’Structural О»вҮҗ                    _ = structural-О»вҮҗ
nE-0вҶ’Structural ПҒвҮ’                    _ = structural-ПҒвҮ’
nE-0вҶ’Structural ПҒвҮҗ                    _ = structural-ПҒвҮҗ
nE-0вҶ’Structural ОұвҮ’                    _ = structural-ОұвҮ’
nE-0вҶ’Structural ОұвҮҗ                    _ = structural-ОұвҮҗ
nE-0вҶ’Structural (Пғ вҰғ s вҰ„)             _ = structural-Пғ вҰғ s вҰ„
nE-0вҶ’Structural (h вҲҳ k) g-nEвүЎ0 =
  -- `nE вҹӘ h вҲҳ k вҹ« = nE вҹӘ k вҹ« + nE вҹӘ h вҹ«` definitionally (see `nE-вҲҳ`
  -- in AtomicCompound.agda вҖ” note the order: it's `nE k + nE h`).
  structural-вҲҳ
    (nE-0вҶ’Structural h (m+nвүЎ0вҮ’nвүЎ0 (nE вҹӘ k вҹ«) g-nEвүЎ0))
    (nE-0вҶ’Structural k (m+nвүЎ0вҮ’mвүЎ0 (nE вҹӘ k вҹ«) g-nEвүЎ0))
nE-0вҶ’Structural (h вҠ—вӮҒ k) g-nEвүЎ0 =
  structural-вҠ—
    (nE-0вҶ’Structural h (m+nвүЎ0вҮ’mвүЎ0 (nE вҹӘ h вҹ«) g-nEвүЎ0))
    (nE-0вҶ’Structural k (m+nвүЎ0вҮ’nвүЎ0 (nE вҹӘ h вҹ«) g-nEвүЎ0))

